The paladin and the shadowknight.<br>
Both are tanks.<br>
One is a defensive tank (Pal)<br>
One is an offensive tank (SK)<br>
<br>
Pal is defensive because our skills are defensive in nature, healing, buffs, root, LoH etc.<br>
SK is offensive because their skills are offensive in nature. DD's, dots, fear, lifetaps, HT etc...<br>
<br>
That's it.<br>
That's why we are the defensive tank. Nowhere in there is there talk of warriors or any other class. <br>
It's just the 2 sides of the coin. <br>
